{"about_the_game":"Striving for Light is a rogue-lite ARPG where you utilise a unique infinite expanding skilltree to fight your way through the darkness, striving for light. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/SfL_gameplay.gif?t=1737379144\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dive into a dark, mysterious world full of dangers<br></li><li>Explore random generated maps and face the dangers that lurk there<br></li><li>Level up and utilise a unique random generated and infinite expanding skill tree<br></li><li>Unlock new skills, weapons, maps and characters<br></li><li>Over 11 unique environments each with unique enemies and bosses to explore<br></li><li>Endgame systems (Rifts, Mapping System, Challenges)<br></li><li>Online leaderboards with seasons and private league system<br></li><li>Local-Coop mode<br></li><li>Hardcore and Softcore mode as well as 5 Difficulty Tiers<br></li><li>Everything is hand drawn<br></li><li>Self-composed Soundtrack (+77 min)</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/skillTree2.gif?t=1737379144\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Skill system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each run gives you a new unique skill tree to explore<br></li><li>Dynamic expanding skilltree depending on your skill pathway<br></li><li>Reforge connections between skill nodes or replace a skill by utilising collectible shards<br></li><li>Collect skillgems and shape your skill tree</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/SfL_crafting.gif?t=1737379144\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gearing &amp; Crafting</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Deep itemisation system <br></li><li>55+ unique weapon bases with randomised stats can be upgraded to legendaries and ascended by crafting <br></li><li>Over 35+ unique trinkets including powerful legendary trinkets <br></li><li>70+ unique skill nodes<br></li><li>8 unique characters with different stats and abilities to shape craft your builds</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/SfLCharacters_big.gif?t=1737379144\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Combat system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenging enemies and boss encounters<br></li><li>Dynamically switch between melee and ranged weapons during fights<br></li><li>Powerful active abilities like shapeshifting and massive attacks<br></li><li>Dual resource system to manage melee and ranged attacks<br></li><li>Dodge system to evade enemy attacks</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/extras/pathfinderEvolve.gif?t=1737379144\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endgame system</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Delve deeper into the darkness and face an ever increasing challenge<br></li><li>Infinite expanding map progression system<br></li><li>Rift Endgame system with separate leader boards<br></li><li>Seasonal Challenges and 5 Difficulty Tiers<br></li><li>Add and alter map modifiers to increase the challenge but also your rewards</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737379144","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/page.bg.jpg?t=1737379144","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/652e4ce65e1116afabfbca77deb3112fcf087a8e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737379144","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646790/652e4ce65e1116afabfbca77deb3112fcf087a8e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737379144","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Sp